11... Nxd4 12. Bxd4 e5
{ If  12...Bc6  13.Bd3  we finish our development and aim to play g4, as usual. }
13. fxe5 dxe5 14. Qg3
{ Again, this tactical motif appears on the board. Do you rememeber it? } *

