13. Be3 Nc5 { Black continues their original idea. } 14. O-O-O
{ For the moment we are not worried about the capture on d3 since after Rxd3 we still have very annoying plans regarding the control of the black squares with moves like Na4. }
14... Nxd3+ 15. Rxd3 a5 { 15...O-O  16.Na4  . } 16. Na4 Ba6
{ 16...dxe4  17.fxe4  . } 17. Rb3
{ With a very nice coordination on the queenside. } *

