{ Si  14...Bc7  15.c3!!  taking advantage of the fact that Black cannot take in good conditions to exert a quick pressure.  15...Rd8  16.Bc4  Bd5 is next with total domination.   15...dxc3?  16.Nxc3  Black cannot allow the knight to join the battle. Nd5 is a huge threat.   14...Be6  the most human move  15.Qh5  intending to go f4 and the rook lift via d3. }
15. Nxb6 axb6 16. g4
{ We want to break on g5 or play Rg1+Rg3 with a double-edged position. } *

