{ 12...Ne5  13.Na4  taking advantage of the fact that the knight on d7 has moved to bring our knight to b6. Besides, we clear the way of our c4-pawn. }
13. axb6 Qxb6 14. Be3
{ Our pieces are ready to exert pressure on the queenside. } *

