{ The bishop is immune due to concrete lines. } 13... Be6 14. Bxe6
{ This leads directly to a very favorable endgame for us.   14.Bg3  the white squares will be very weak after the trade. }
14... fxe6 15. Qxe6+ Qe7 16. Qxe7+ Bxe7 17. Bg3
{ White is a pawn up, and we will continue with moves such as O-O-O and Kb1 with an advantage. }
