10... d5 { 10...Be7  11.h4  intending to go g5 next. } 11. O-O-O Bb7
{ Si  11...Bb4  12.Bd4  this reply against ...Bb4 must be engraved in your head. }
12. h4
{ Due to the fact that we are better developed, we are in good conditions to attack and exploit BLack's king position in the middle of the board. }
