{ The knight will enter on g7 to destabilize the king for good. } 10... Qa5 11.
Nxg7+ Kd8 { 11...Kf8  12.Bh6  . } 12. Qf3
{ Sacrificing the knight, but bringing our forces to tha attack. If f7 falls, so does Black's position. }
