{ If  9...d5  10.c4  . } 10. f4 Nd7 11. Nxe6
{ Opening everything up to exploit our advantage in development. } 11... fxe6
12. Qh5+ Kd8 13. Ne4 { The knight heads to g5 with catastrophic consequences. }
*

