{ It makes sense to offer Black to go for the endgame to avoid unnecessary complications. }
11... Qxf3 12. Nxf3 Bb7 13. Nxa8 Bxa8 14. Be2
{ We have an exchange for a pawn and with no weaknesses in our camp. } *

