{ Black has had to bring his queen this far to avoid a check on c7. } 11. Bd3
{ Exerting pressure quickly on the very loose e4-knight. } 11... d5 12. exd6
O-O 13. O-O Nxd6 14. Nxd6 exd6 15. Bf4
{ Black has a disastrous version of an IQP -isolated queen's pawn- position, as they have no development at all. Re1 is coming next. }
